40|$|Debugging and {{protocol}} {{conformance testing}} of power <b>meter</b> <b>reading</b> system {{which is based}} on wireless sensor network is complex, aiming at this problem, we develop a powerful, flexible use, convenient carrying multichannel real-time data monitoring and transmitting device in this paper. The hardware realization and working principle of multichannel synchronous data transceiver are introduced in detail. On this basis, its hardware scheme and software flow for wireless <b>meter</b> <b>reading</b> network are designed. The tests show that, the device is with good real-timeand high stability which is a good debugging and testing device for wireless <b>meter</b> <b>reading</b> network...|$|R
